===Letter===
'''צ''' (spelled ''[[sadhe]]'') is the eighteenth letter of the [[Hebrew]] alphabet.<br>
'''ץ''' is the final form of the letter ([[sofeet]]), used only at the end of a word.

צ also represents the [[numeral]] 90 in Hebrew numbering.

* '''Last''': [[פ]]
* '''Next''': [[ק]]

